No. 09-1009 (R46-020). Ulises Francisco Martinez Silva, et al., Petitioners v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 560 U.S. 980, 130 S. Ct. 3449,

177 L. Ed. 2d 353,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4979. June 16, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to this Court’s Rule 46.

Same case below, 329 Fed. Appx. 142.
